  "narratives": {
    "full_description": "Presentation of eBAU, an artist’s book of thoughts and visions for the New European Bauhaus by Roberto Paci Dalò\n\nCreated under invitation of the European Commission, eBAU is a collection of thoughts and ideas on what the New European Bauhaus could be. It is not an essay, nor a manifesto, but a series of artistic suggestions morphing into fleeting visions.\n\nRoberto Paci Dalò shares his insights through unique drawings and texts, presenting an artist’s book designed to point toward the other realities that are ours to invent.",
